metadata.title: Cen-Tec Systems 35301 Vacuum Attachment, 1.25" Upholstery Tool, Black
features: This vacuum accessory will fit all major canister vacuums, upright vacuums and central vacuum brands with 1.25 inch connections
The brush helps release embedded dirt in furniture or deeper carpets
The tool also includes a brush strip for surface cleaning for carpets
Compatible with major brands of central vac, including beam, nutone, electrolux, hayden, vacumaid, aggressor, vacuflo, md, canavac, cyclovac, air vac
description: The 35301 premium upholstery tool won't seal to the floor or furniture, keeping the air flow necessary for effective cleaning. The brush helps release embedded dirt in furniture or deeper carpets. The tool also includes a brush strip for surface cleaning for carpets. The 35301 includes a molded insert and is Black in color.
